INSERT INTO `tbl_master` VALUES (1,'<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">WELCOME,</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>MMPCONS</strong> is a tax consulting firm dedicated to provide innovative and best solutions for clients&acirc;&euro;&trade; tax problems and business needs. We offer a broad range of tax services performed by our highly skilled and experienced professionals that strive to exceed all of our clients&acirc;&euro;&trade; expectation </span></p>','<div class=\"content\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n<h1><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Services,</span></h1>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Our services cover :</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Monthly &amp; Annual Tax Return</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Assistance in Tax Audit, Objection &amp; Appeal</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Comprehensive Tax Review</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Tax Planning</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Day to Day Tax Advisory Services</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">International Tax Services</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Tax Administration</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Tax Training, Workshop, Seminar &amp; Research</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Monthly &amp; Annual Tax Return</strong></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">We help clients in preparing and submitting monthly and annual employee income tax returns, monthly VAT returns, monthly withholding tax return, annual corporate tax return and annual individual income tax return timely and accurately.</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Assistance in Tax Audit, Objection &amp; Appeal</strong></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">We assist and represent clients in dealing with audits conducted by tax authorities and subsequent objections and appeals against tax assessments. Our tax professionals will provide effective strategies on such actions, including the filing of all necessary documents and facts to support our strong and valid argumentations for defense.</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Comprehensive Tax Review<br /></strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">This service is aimed to ensure that clients have continuously maintained the compliance with tax provisions. We will review, test and diagnose clients&rsquo; financial records and related documents to identify such improper tax treatments that might give rise to any tax penalties and potential tax burden. This service will come up with our excellent suggestions and recommendations to cope with.</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Tax Planning</strong></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">We provide tax-planning and design that meet clients&rsquo; business needs. We help clients in optimizing tax benefit of mergers &amp; acquisitions, restructurings, direct / indirect capital investment (domestic / offshore) and financing arrangement. We always help our clients in achieving their goals in a way that will legally minimize their tax liability and get tax benefits without having to evade and break tax laws.</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Day to Day Tax Advisory Services</strong></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">We serve clients on day-to-day basis in the form of correspondence and verbal communication, including meeting, telephone conversation, fax and e-mail for any general and specific tax cases at any time of the clients&rsquo; request. In addition, we will update clients through email or fax for any new tax regulations particularly for such rules that will give direct impact to the tax obligation of clients.</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>International Tax Services</strong></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">We are expert in dealing with international taxation issues such as transfer pricing, taxation of expatriates, joint venture and overseas joint operation project, taxation of foreign-source income, application of tax treaties, international tax planning and any other issues on taxation of cross-border transactions.</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Tax Administration</strong></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">We help clients for the registration and revocation of Tax Identification Number (NPWP), the application for a tax clearance certificate and other tax administration matters.</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Tax Training, Workshop, Seminar &amp; Research</strong></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">This service includes in-house tax trainings and workshops that are intended to improve the skill and knowledge of participants in both domestic and international taxation. We provide not only general training for all kinds of taxes but also specific tax topics for specific industries based on clients&rsquo; needs. We also provide seminars for any current and relevant issues in tax legislations and practices. In addition, we do tax research for specific purposes.</span></p>\r\n</div>','<h1><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Clients,</span></h1>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: small; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Our clients come from a wide range of fields including charter flight, oil palm plantation, construction, law firm, education foundation, information technology, freight forwarding, chemical and pharmacy traiding, precast concrete industry and healthcare institution.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">A partial list of our clients includes :</span></p>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 15.75pt;\">\r\n<td width=\"263\" height=\"21\"><span style=\"font-size: small; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&bull; PT. Airfast Indonesia</span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: small; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&bull; PT. CCM Indonesia</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"h